sentences: Jay Migliori (November 14, 1930 â€“ September 2, 2001) was an American saxophonist, best known as a founding member of Supersax, a tribute band to Charlie Parker.
Migliori started playing the saxophone after he received one as a birthday present at the age of twelve.
He made his first recording in 1955, and soon joined up with Woody Herman's band.
In 1972, he would become a member of Supersax, a nine-piece band (featuring five saxophones) that was started by saxophonist Med Flory and bassist Buddy Clark.
